TEXT(&beginproblem);
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,9,1);
$b = random(2,9,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Algebraically find the inverse function of \(f(x)=$a x+$b\).
$BR  
\(f^{-1}(x)= \) \{ ans_rule(20) \}
$BR  
EOT

$ans1 = "(x-$b)/$a";
&ANS(fun_cmp($ans1));

